title: Otome Danshi Ni Koisuru Otome
alternative_title: A maiden in love with a man-in-drag ; 乙女男子に恋する乙女
status: A maiden in love with a man-in-drag ; 乙女男子に恋する乙女
description:
Description :
        A 30 episodes short comic by Shimazaki Mujirushi

Mizuguchi Mayu, a girl who hates men, fell in love at first sight with a... "man-in-drag"!?
Does she likes "girls"? Or does she likes "boys"?
Find out in this heart throbbing pure love comedy! (from twi4)
